QuestData.Title: Ashran Dominance
QuestData.Description: As we feared the Horde are trying to consolidate their position here on the island by looting it, just like we feared. Get out there and show them the Alliance won't put up with their aggression.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Volrath leads the Horde forces in Ashran.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat the Horde at all event locations in Ashran and kill High Warlord Volrath.
